edia": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Remember when Trump was laughed at by a German delegation for denouncing them for their dependence on Russian gas?\r\n\r\nIn the last year;\r\n\r\nBMW : -21.42%\r\nVW: -16%\r\nMercedes: -8.4%\r\n\r\nMeanwhile;\r\n\r\nGeneral Motors : +46.66%\r\nTesla : +33.85%", "last_comment_created": 1783372496225, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 7, "score_up": 336, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 21, "created": 1783327268000, "id": "2074051005465915637", "video": {"preview": "https://pbs.twimg.com/amplify_video_thumb/2074050301405921280/img/CtUngIaWa2ah1CrA.jpg", "mpeg": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2074050301405921280/pl/SciE9gpOgd_W6pPp.m3u8?v=3dd", "aspectRatio": [16, 9], "heightRatio": 56, "type": "video/mp4", "url": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2074050301405921280/vid/avc1/480x270/O2rwlPodlJ_Bn40s.mp4"}, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2006331556206403584/9XLTnrOV_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Andy", "username": "PositivFuturist"}, "content": "Remember when Trump was laughed at by a German delegation for denouncing them for their dependence on Russian gas?\n\nIn the last year;\n\nBMW : -21.42%\nVW: -16%\nMercedes: -8.4%\n\nMeanwhile;\n\nGeneral Motors : +46.66%\nTesla : +33.85%\n\nI wonder if they're still laughing.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 389}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBlyZcdc", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 181, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8715828, "raw_content": "A friend of mine and I talk about a lot of stuff, and politics has managed to be civil. Well, the other day, I was told blah blah blah about white male privilege, etc.\n\nI reminded him how they grew up in a two-parent household, graduated with a college degree completely paid for with scholarships, and this country has given him everything all while claiming to be oppressed.\n\nCompared to myself who was in and out of children's centers, group homes, and the foster care system; whose family was ruined by drugs; who joined the military out of high school; deployed to two rat holes; who chose to go into robotics; who worked in addition to using his GI Bill to make sure that he could one day have a good life; never got a criminal record; converted to Christianity after years of reading and listening; accepted Jesus Christ.\n\nI worked hard for everything, but I won't pretend that it's not at least a little bit insulting to hear your friend tell you that you actually didn't. But, I thank God for what I have been blessed with, and for Him blessing me with the gift of tenacity, and the insight to say to myself, \"I want better for myself and for my family one day.\"\n\nBut apparently, that hard work will mean nothing to him. I told him that he is perfectly within his right to hate white men. I am simply going to leave them to their own devices.", "author": "SarsourCuntReturns", "created": 1783350928216, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Nellie_the_Beaut", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "23-Year Friendship Destroyed Because of Woke Ideology - Screw this Ideological Cancer", "last_comment_created": 1783375939844, "content": "<p>A friend of mine and I talk about a lot of stuff, and politics has managed to be civil. Well, the other day, I was told blah blah blah about white male privilege, etc.</p>\n<p>I reminded him how they grew up in a two-parent household, graduated with a college degree completely paid for with scholarships, and this country has given him everything all while claiming to be oppressed.</p>\n<p>Compared to myself who was in and out of children's centers, group homes, and the foster care system; whose family was ruined by drugs; who joined the military out of high school; deployed to two rat holes; who chose to go into robotics; who worked in addition to using his GI Bill to make sure that he could one day have a good life; never got a criminal record; converted to Christianity after years of reading and listening; accepted Jesus Christ.</p>\n<p>I worked hard for everything, but I won't pretend that it's not at least a little bit insulting to hear your friend tell you that you actually didn't. But, I thank God for what I have been blessed with, and for Him blessing me with the gift of tenacity, and the insight to say to myself, &quot;I want better for myself and for my family one day.&quot;</p>\n<p>But apparently, that hard work will mean nothing to him. I told him that he is perfectly within his right to hate white men. I am simply going to leave them to their own devices.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 36, "score_up": 181, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2073880851335549203", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBlzfoxx", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 107, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8716055, "raw_content": "", "author": "KuzoKevin", "created": 1783361194241, "profile_picture": "", "communit